{"tid":1661304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍於浸大校門前設10多監控鏡頭 上課學生感不安 錢大康亦於校內增設鏡頭","createTime":"2019-10-18T04:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T03:20:43.000Z","uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"62c6503482dd01e5236df6e64afe715b0b8fa293","tid":1661304,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/3353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F3353&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=46c65b64\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/3353</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/192A5F61-E764-4E3B-A923-5A7840086738.jpeg?zoom=1.100000023841858&amp;resize=1140%2C855&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F192A5F61-E764-4E3B-A923-5A7840086738.jpeg%3Fzoom%3D1.100000023841858%26resize%3D1140%252C855%26ssl%3D1&h=49052cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每個鏡頭對准行人路，預計可以攝入每個路過師生嘅臉孔。<br />\n隨着反送中運動持續升溫，鄰近香港浸會大學嘅駐港解放軍軍營喺10月頭開始增設監控鏡頭，肉眼可見已經有10幾個豎立喺往返校園路附近。<br />\n<br />\n錢大康喺星期一（14號）「與管理層心靈對話會」上，突然透露會增加監控鏡頭，除咗要保障學生安全，更加要防止有人喺教學樓擲物至鄰近嘅解放軍軍營。佢又聲稱，有唔少大陸學生同佢反映，擔心喺校園嘅人身安全，因為多咗好多著黑衫嘅人出入，希望增加保安人手。佢昨日用電郵公布校園新保安措施，如邀請「外人」審視校園潛在危險。<br />\n<br />\n同學表示，除咗喺聯福道、禧福道同聯合道，即同學來往浸大校園嘅主要通道設有監控鏡頭外，軍營鐵絲網後亦多咗軍人駐守，監視路過同學嘅一舉一動。<br />\n<br />\n錢大康電郵全文及相關報道：<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/3350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F3350&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=0c5f2c10\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/3350</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/F441DC4A-1226-404F-80DF-4BB11BB0A242.jpeg?w=634&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FF441DC4A-1226-404F-80DF-4BB11BB0A242.jpeg%3Fw%3D634%26ssl%3D1&h=7aa15410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n浸大同學喺HKBU Secrets發問，指感到不安，詢問近日出現嘅監控鏡頭有冇人面識別功能。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/94899B60-EA2A-41EE-8677-2AAECA2E7D46.jpeg?w=528&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F94899B60-EA2A-41EE-8677-2AAECA2E7D46.jpeg%3Fw%3D528%26ssl%3D1&h=71ff7d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2C10520A-C4A2-4A08-8C51-524AE1DF8DAB.jpeg?zoom=1.100000023841858&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F2C10520A-C4A2-4A08-8C51-524AE1DF8DAB.jpeg%3Fzoom%3D1.100000023841858%26ssl%3D1&h=879264f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5aa730a7f036f147114b543f93cd1fea550a017d","tid":1661304,"uid":68669,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"起幾多cctv都無用啦，關鍵時候就一定壞or整唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274471784e1093e8a97e059ddea77def757e6c7b","tid":1661304,"uid":113922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:35:39.000Z","msg":"裝修"},{"pid":"eee3a1a675c354e1560bd43d8588e9492bb253a4","tid":1661304,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"【FC】西九站遊行係中共真春袋！<span style=\"color: red;\">需要針對強國文宣<strong>輸出革命</strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>消息人士表示，7月7日過10萬人去到高鐵西九龍站後，「中國國家安全委員會」就對西九龍站「突發」事件設定了「專案」，就各種事況的發生計劃了處理辦法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661232</a>"},{"pid":"380cf846b69d9ce776336453cc519fb9946a7a7b","tid":1661304,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5aa730a7f036f147114b543f93cd1fea550a017d","tid":1661304,"uid":68669,"like":11,"dislike":0,"sco